Comment: 0,0:02:09.78,0:02:11.78,ZH-Main-Down,,0,0,0,,正文
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.78,0:02:13.65,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,哇 好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.23,0:02:16.00,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,好厲害的水光
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.00,0:02:17.48,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,這裡是高麗川嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.48,0:02:20.55,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,吾野出來竟然是這樣的風景啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.55,0:02:22.18,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,無憂無慮
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.18,0:02:23.07,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.07,0:02:24.74,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,小晶你別破壞氣氛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.06,0:02:26.96,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,其實你也是很激動的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.96,0:02:29.09,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,不看著你的臉真看不出來呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.09,0:02:31.18,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,激動怎麼可能表現在臉上
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.18,0:02:32.34,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,突然就跑出來了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.34,0:02:34.26,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,你那雙手是怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.54,0:02:35.73,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.73,0:02:37.03,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,別過來
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.03,0:02:39.17,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,揉揉×N
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.43,0:02:41.83,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,真的是 你們兩個
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.58,0:02:47.48,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,吶 池袋要多久才到呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.48,0:02:48.27,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,朝發夕至嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.27,0:02:50.62,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,連黑豹車隊都到不了的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.62,0:02:52.22,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,明天肯定不行
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.22,0:02:52.92,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,欸
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.92,0:02:55.46,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,但是之前只花了一個小時就到了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.46,0:02:57.75,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,就算現在比以前「拉伸」了不少
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.75,0:02:59.43,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,但也沒什麼到達不了的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.43,0:03:00.68,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,你這太樂觀了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.68,0:03:03.18,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,要是就這麼無憂無慮毫無計劃地過去
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.18,0:03:05.90,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,十有八九會在某個地方被團滅的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.90,0:03:06.91,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,聽我說
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.91,0:03:09.38,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,要這麼說 可能明天早上突然就發現 啊嘞
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.38,0:03:11.40,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,我已經到達池袋了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.40,0:03:13.12,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,或許不是明天就到 而是需要三天呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.12,0:03:14.61,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,根本不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.61,0:03:16.73,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,最快也應該需要一個月
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.73,0:03:17.81,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,可能更多
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.81,0:03:18.70,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,那就半個月
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.70,0:03:19.50,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,三個月
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.50,0:03:20.32,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,對了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.32,0:03:22.54,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,靜留肯定會考慮到這一點的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.54,0:03:23.60,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,聽聽她怎麼說
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.60,0:03:24.89,ZH-Main-Down,Group,0,0,0,,吶 到達需要幾天呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.89,0:03:26.15,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,分心駕駛很危險的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.57,0:03:30.14,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,好了 靜留剛剛學會開火車
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.14,0:03:30.65,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.31,0:03:37.85,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,靜留 車速是不是太快了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.34,0:03:43.08,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,果然速度太快了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.08,0:03:45.19,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,能不能放緩一點呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.19,0:03:46.37,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,我在努力
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.37,0:03:46.79,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,欸
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.10,0:03:49.65,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,我雖然在努力 但速度根本降不下來
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.65,0:03:50.66,ZH-Main-Down,Group,0,0,0,,欸
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.79,0:03:53.59,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,彎道
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.59,0:03:54.58,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,彎道 彎道
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.74,0:03:57.38,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,又是彎道
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.62,0:03:59.96,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,彎道×N
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.72,0:04:03.68,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,超彎的路
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.01,0:04:07.74,ZH-Main-Down,Group,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.68,0:04:18.51,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,我以為要死了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.51,0:04:20.32,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,真實感覺「勿忘你終有一死」
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.32,0:04:22.90,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,你沒事了嗎 靜留
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.90,0:04:23.78,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,大概
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.18,0:04:28.66,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,善治郎教我的時候 我以為是很簡單的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.00,0:04:30.48,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,善治郎先生
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.48,0:04:31.92,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,他突然變回正常人了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.92,0:04:33.75,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,雖然每天只有五分鐘
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.75,0:04:34.53,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,然後就教我
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.53,0:04:35.38,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,欸
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.38,0:04:36.14,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.14,0:04:37.32,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,真的 是真的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.32,0:04:38.32,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,而且還變成了一個帥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.32,0:04:39.17,ZH-Main-Down,Group,0,0,0,,帥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.17,0:04:41.11,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,靜留 說謊是不行的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.11,0:04:42.92,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,不是 我說的是真的 絕對真實
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.92,0:04:45.01,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,不然我怎麼學會開火車的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.01,0:04:48.17,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,善治郎先生之前可是鐵道公司的精英
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.17,0:04:50.23,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,我以為只是吹牛來著
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.23,0:04:51.22,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,但竟然是真的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.22,0:04:53.57,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,五分鐘能夠變回來 是什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.57,0:04:55.60,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,是帽子 駕駛員的帽子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.60,0:04:57.11,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,把它給他戴上之後就變回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.11,0:04:58.94,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,聽我說 靜留
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.94,0:05:00.88,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,說謊是真的不行哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.88,0:05:02.04,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,我發四我發四
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.04,0:05:03.07,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,絕對是真的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.07,0:05:05.06,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,不然我絕對不會開火車的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.06,0:05:06.25,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,Trust Me
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.25,0:05:09.54,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,再說了 你是真的開往池袋嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.54,0:05:11.18,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,我們沒有走錯方向吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.18,0:05:11.69,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,哈
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.46,0:05:14.57,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,那邊是秩父市對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.57,0:05:16.60,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,所以這邊就是往池袋的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.60,0:05:18.17,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,噢 原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.17,0:05:19.07,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.07,0:05:23.07,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,聽說池袋 有模特兒和執事管家對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.07,0:05:25.67,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,還有偵探什麼的 殺人犯之類的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.67,0:05:29.00,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,要是麻痺大意 被刺 被拐 被騙都可能
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.00,0:05:31.39,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,痛痛癢癢 時髦流行
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.39,0:05:33.39,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,這是什麼刻板印象
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.39,0:05:35.09,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,還要提防宰客行為噢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.09,0:05:35.58,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,欸
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.58,0:05:36.59,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,玲實 你有帶錢嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.59,0:05:37.86,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,那當然的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.86,0:05:39.16,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,我可是好好存起來的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.16,0:05:39.86,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.86,0:05:41.53,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,挺好 有多少
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.53,0:05:42.94,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,我的儲蓄罐啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.94,0:05:43.72,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,有兩萬日元嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.72,0:05:45.96,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,不對 我的儲蓄罐
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.96,0:05:47.41,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,怎麼了 玲實
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.68,0:05:49.06,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,{\an8}我的儲蓄罐落在家裡了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.41,0:05:49.06,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,噢 她忘在家裡了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.06,0:05:50.83,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,我一共就兩百五十日元
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.83,0:05:51.53,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,好少
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.53,0:05:52.50,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,小晶呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.50,0:05:54.22,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,小晶你帶了多少錢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.22,0:05:56.58,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,個人資訊是不會告訴你的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.58,0:05:58.03,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,讓我借用一點嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.03,0:05:59.88,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,借貸什麼的我不要啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.88,0:06:00.59,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,小柒
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.87,0:06:03.50,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,我倒是帶了點錢 可以借給你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.50,0:06:04.15,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.15,0:06:05.29,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,靜留你是我的神
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.29,0:06:06.22,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,你能借我多少呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.22,0:06:09.19,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,我就帶了三千多日元 借你一千吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.19,0:06:09.95,ZH-Main-Down,Group,0,0,0,,好少
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.95,0:06:11.09,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,別扯 這可是巨款
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.09,0:06:12.66,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,這上面寫了什麼鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.66,0:06:14.69,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,如果沒有麵包 就買點零食吃
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.69,0:06:16.50,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,稍微感覺有些不同
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.50,0:06:18.30,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,遠水救不了近火
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.30,0:06:19.81,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,就是就是 就那種感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.81,0:06:20.94,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,才不是這種感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.94,0:06:22.70,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,有一千二百五十日元
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.70,0:06:23.73,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,要買些什麼東西呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.73,0:06:25.33,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,首先還是先買點能吃的食物吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.33,0:06:27.45,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,啊 我想買點奶茶之類喝喝
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.45,0:06:30.58,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,還有來份奶油蒜香燒雞 還有法式吐司
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.58,0:06:32.38,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,不是這些 要更加普通的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.38,0:06:34.03,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,買點罐頭食品或是罐裝麵包
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.03,0:06:35.54,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,欸 好無聊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.54,0:06:37.08,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,撫子 你莫得夢想
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.08,0:06:39.49,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,但是我們什麼都沒有攜帶
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.49,0:06:40.15,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,欸
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.15,0:06:42.05,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,我們放學之後就直接上來了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.80,0:06:44.34,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,確實
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.34,0:06:46.06,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,我們沒有任何吃的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.06,0:06:47.70,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,稍微一點的話 我還是有的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.70,0:06:48.81,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,真的嗎 太棒啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.81,0:06:49.69,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.69,0:06:51.66,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,我說了要做好準備的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.66,0:06:52.59,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,能看看嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.59,0:06:53.44,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,嗯 看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.44,0:06:57.46,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,果然生存 需要最低限度的準備
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.46,0:06:58.22,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,這什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.22,0:06:59.48,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,香板
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.48,0:07:00.70,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,你不知道嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.70,0:07:02.33,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,這是用來量取義大利麵的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.33,0:07:03.99,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,所以哪裡有所謂的「義大利麵」
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.99,0:07:05.85,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,這是練習穿的蘇醬
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.85,0:07:06.60,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,確實
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.60,0:07:08.43,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,為什麼靜留你帶著這件啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.43,0:07:10.39,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,哦 我在我家裡找到的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.02,0:07:10.39,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,{\an8}讓我看看 撫子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.39,0:07:11.62,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,給我給我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.62,0:07:12.26,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,嘛 我沒什麼問題
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.26,0:07:12.85,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,駁回
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.85,0:07:14.17,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,我得到的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.38,0:07:15.56,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,{\an8}吵架禁止 要好好相處
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.83,0:07:19.06,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,靜留 食物只剩下這麼多了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.06,0:07:19.84,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,啊嘞
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.18,0:07:22.62,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,我記得我帶了很多的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.62,0:07:23.58,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,還有就是那些
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.58,0:07:25.05,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,啊 苦瓜
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.05,0:07:26.85,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,畢竟是吾野的特產
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.85,0:07:29.22,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,咱不是很喜歡它
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.23,0:07:32.24,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,啊 我他媽在做什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.24,0:07:32.94,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,太興奮了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.94,0:07:34.71,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,真的是 我不知道該怎麼辦了敲
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.71,0:07:36.45,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,啊 這種事情確實
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.45,0:07:38.14,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,「視野強化」什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.14,0:07:40.00,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,沒有比這更好的機會了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.00,0:07:42.02,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,要是能列個清單的話 應該就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.87,0:07:43.99,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,那個
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.32,0:07:47.44,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,我們的財產 這些就是全部了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.97,0:07:50.52,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,問題是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.52,0:07:51.58,ZH-Main-Down,Group,0,0,0,,問題
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.98,0:07:53.37,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,內褲怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.37,0:07:54.29,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,這啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.29,0:07:55.12,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,內褲啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.12,0:07:57.78,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,女孩子什麼的 不要說什麼內褲啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.78,0:07:58.61,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,那就底褲
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.61,0:07:59.44,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,不是這個意思啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.44,0:08:03.09,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,但實際上 我們不知道要多久才能到池袋
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.09,0:08:04.57,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,一直就這樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.57,0:08:07.91,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,卡斯蒂利亞女王伊莎貝爾 祈禱戰爭的勝利
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.91,0:08:10.58,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,說是九個月都沒有更換過內褲
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.58,0:08:13.16,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,要是買不到的話 被葉香看見會被說教的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.16,0:08:14.80,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,靜留 你冷靜一點
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.80,0:08:16.04,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,欸 好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.04,0:08:18.54,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,等到了東吾野後 再去買吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.54,0:08:20.84,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,還要去儲備一些食物
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.84,0:08:22.04,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,而且可以長期保存的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.04,0:08:23.44,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,我肚子餓啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.44,0:08:23.72,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.72,0:08:24.95,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,你想死嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.95,0:08:28.00,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,在生存恐怖遊戲中 食慾貪婪的胖子最先死
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.00,0:08:28.82,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,我才不胖
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.82,0:08:30.28,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,稍微忍耐一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.28,0:08:31.48,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,就只是現在嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.48,0:08:32.82,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,忍耐啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.82,0:08:33.87,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,我不擅長
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.72,0:08:37.70,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,反正小晶你會說「我是最難伺候的一個吧」
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.70,0:08:39.62,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,噢哦 被你搶先說啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.62,0:08:40.97,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,有勇氣屈服啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.97,0:08:41.71,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,你說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.71,0:08:42.91,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,冷靜下來
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.04,0:08:52.34,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,還沒有到嗎 池袋
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.34,0:08:54.15,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,這問題問了多少次了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.15,0:08:54.93,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,這有什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.93,0:08:56.37,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,我很在意而已
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.37,0:08:57.90,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,你腦袋是真的笨蛋嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.09,0:09:02.51,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,你這種高高在上的態度真的太壞了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.51,0:09:04.49,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,小晶小晶 眼淚汪晶晶
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.49,0:09:07.67,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,就算我是愛哭鬼 那也是十年之前的事情了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.67,0:09:08.27,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,哼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.27,0:09:09.81,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,零分玲實靈長類
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.81,0:09:11.60,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,我就考過一次零分
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.60,0:09:12.64,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,而且還是小測
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.64,0:09:14.52,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,真的是 你們兩個別吵了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.52,0:09:16.99,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,既然你那麼討厭 就在吾野等著算了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.99,0:09:18.26,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,我又沒有說我討厭
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.26,0:09:19.72,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,不要擅自給我作主
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.83,0:09:21.26,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,{\an8}小晶 玲實
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.72,0:09:21.77,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,小晶你不也自己選擇乘坐這輛列車了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.77,0:09:24.62,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,要不是玲實和撫子上來了 我才不會坐這班車的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.62,0:09:27.42,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,那個是 在那個時間節點迫不得已的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.42,0:09:28.61,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,大家都這樣做的 不是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.61,0:09:30.51,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,你們沒有必要跟我來的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.64,0:09:36.30,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,我原本就打算自己一個人過去的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.25,0:09:40.37,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,就算靜留你這麼說
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.55,0:09:46.07,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,苦瓜
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.07,0:09:48.66,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,總感覺比平常生長得更快
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.99,0:09:51.06,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,還有 霧氣也濃起來了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.06,0:09:52.51,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,這裡是哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.51,0:09:55.04,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,不要告訴我已經過了東吾野了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.75,0:10:07.75,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,玲實 你視力挺好的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.75,0:10:09.35,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,你能看清楚那邊有什麼嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.35,0:10:10.93,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,什麼 你說什麼恐怖的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.93,0:10:12.12,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,那邊的話
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.62,0:10:15.11,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,有什麼呢 感覺沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.11,0:10:15.59,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,欸
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.04,0:10:17.00,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,那是什麼鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.00,0:10:17.81,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.12,0:10:19.25,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,有什麼東西要來了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.25,0:10:20.58,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,什麼是什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.58,0:10:21.59,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,那個是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.59,0:10:22.61,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,是高麗水怪
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.61,0:10:23.56,ZH-Main-Down,Group,0,0,0,,高麗水怪
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.56,0:10:27.15,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,是高麗川現存的 傳說中的神秘龍首
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.34,0:10:32.10,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.61,0:10:33.98,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,是高麗水怪
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.25,0:10:37.94,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,竟然是高麗水怪
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.98,0:10:51.37,ZH-Main-Down,Swan Hermit,0,0,0,,這竟然 是電車啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.23,0:10:55.71,ZH-Main-Down,Swan Hermit,0,0,0,,你們到底是什麼人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.71,0:10:56.71,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,小心
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.71,0:10:58.58,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,他絕對是殺人魔鬼來了結我們的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.58,0:10:59.47,ZH-Main-Down,Swan Hermit,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.47,0:11:03.10,ZH-Main-Down,Swan Hermit,0,0,0,,我就是高麗川史上最強的連環殺人兇手
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.10,0:11:04.69,ZH-Main-Down,Swan Hermit,0,0,0,,喂 你太無禮了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.51,0:11:10.90,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,那個 你是哪位
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.90,0:11:12.88,ZH-Main-Down,Swan Hermit,0,0,0,,我的名字並不重要
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.27,0:11:18.53,ZH-Main-Down,Swan Hermit,0,0,0,,呀嘛 那個 我是說
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.53,0:11:22.86,ZH-Main-Down,Swan Hermit,0,0,0,,我在高麗川來回穿梭 研究並記錄了很多資訊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.86,0:11:26.06,ZH-Main-Down,Swan Hermit,0,0,0,,好久沒有見到任何人了 真的嚇我一跳
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.06,0:11:28.27,ZH-Main-Down,Swan Hermit,0,0,0,,那什麼 你們在做什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.27,0:11:31.35,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,欸 我們 打算前往池袋來著
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.35,0:11:32.76,ZH-Main-Down,Swan Hermit,0,0,0,,欸 池袋啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.76,0:11:33.47,ZH-Main-Down,Swan Hermit,0,0,0,,這確實厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.47,0:11:35.43,ZH-Main-Down,Swan Hermit,0,0,0,,我可是從池袋過來這邊的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.43,0:11:36.54,ZH-Main-Down,Swan Hermit,0,0,0,,我感覺你大有可為…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.54,0:11:37.28,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.50,0:11:39.61,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,你從池袋來的嗎 好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.61,0:11:41.71,ZH-Main-Down,Swan Hermit,0,0,0,,呀 也沒有那麼厲害啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.71,0:11:44.39,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,池袋來的人我是第一次見啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.39,0:11:45.64,ZH-Main-Down,Swan Hermit,0,0,0,,呃 真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.64,0:11:48.20,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,西部呢 東部呢 中池袋公園呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.20,0:11:49.71,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,池袋公車 動畫怎麼樣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.71,0:11:51.56,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,淳久堂書店呢 三省堂書店呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.56,0:11:52.57,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,還有奶茶呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.57,0:11:54.15,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,現在最熱門的咖啡店呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.35,0:11:55.47,ZH-Main-Down,Swan Hermit,0,0,0,,這個嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.47,0:11:56.36,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,嘛什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.36,0:11:57.11,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,你原來不知道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.21,0:11:59.43,ZH-Main-Down,Swan Hermit,0,0,0,,請等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.43,0:12:02.76,ZH-Main-Down,Swan Hermit,0,0,0,,但是有一件事情是可以確定的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.76,0:12:04.06,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,欸 什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.32,0:12:06.49,ZH-Main-Down,Swan Hermit,0,0,0,,那就是7G事件
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.49,0:12:10.35,ZH-Main-Down,Swan Hermit,0,0,0,,那之後 沿著西部池袋線以外的世界全部都消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.35,0:12:11.01,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,欸
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.01,0:12:14.37,ZH-Main-Down,Swan Hermit,0,0,0,,如上 咱是推測大概感覺出來的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.37,0:12:16.84,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,推測 大概 感覺出來的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.84,0:12:17.82,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,到底是哪個啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.82,0:12:20.63,ZH-Main-Down,Swan Hermit,0,0,0,,東邊的菌類高聳入雲
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.63,0:12:22.69,ZH-Main-Down,Swan Hermit,0,0,0,,高調宣言要去征服
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.69,0:12:24.17,ZH-Main-Down,Swan Hermit,0,0,0,,而再往東邊的話
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.17,0:12:28.63,ZH-Main-Down,Swan Hermit,0,0,0,,與山羊共存的野獸之名雖有所不同 但正是我要說明的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.63,0:12:29.85,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,所以到底是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.85,0:12:30.59,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,你到底想要說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.59,0:12:31.42,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,原來是那個
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.42,0:12:33.32,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,無理荒誕的自我獨白
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.32,0:12:34.24,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,啊 是這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.24,0:12:36.50,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,所以才感覺這麼誇張啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.50,0:12:37.74,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,我們應該走了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.74,0:12:38.33,ZH-Main-Down,Swan Hermit,0,0,0,,欸
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.33,0:12:40.25,ZH-Main-Down,Swan Hermit,0,0,0,,欸等會 等會等會等會
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.25,0:12:44.40,ZH-Main-Down,Swan Hermit,0,0,0,,總而言之 我不建議你們前去池袋啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.40,0:12:45.39,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.39,0:12:49.87,ZH-Main-Down,Swan Hermit,0,0,0,,總而言之這非常 非常地非常 非常不可能 我推測
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.87,0:12:51.32,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,如上是你所認為的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.32,0:12:52.34,ZH-Main-Down,Swan Hermit,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.79,0:12:53.66,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,好 我們走
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.66,0:12:54.63,ZH-Main-Down,Swan Hermit,0,0,0,,敲 等會
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.22,0:12:57.74,ZH-Main-Down,Swan Hermit,0,0,0,,機會難得 稍微給我些什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.74,0:12:59.84,ZH-Main-Down,Swan Hermit,0,0,0,,來點禮物嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.81,0:13:02.80,ZH-Main-Down,Swan Hermit,0,0,0,,我給你好東西
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.80,0:13:03.67,ZH-Main-Down,Swan Hermit,0,0,0,,交換
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.67,0:13:04.67,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,好東西是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.67,0:13:06.64,ZH-Main-Down,Swan Hermit,0,0,0,,這個是我自己做的地圖
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.64,0:13:07.86,ZH-Main-Down,Swan Hermit,0,0,0,,它超級有用的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.86,0:13:08.85,ZH-Main-Down,Swan Hermit,0,0,0,,我超推薦的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.85,0:13:10.35,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,哦 謝了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.35,0:13:11.56,ZH-Main-Down,Swan Hermit,0,0,0,,還有一句勸告
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.56,0:13:13.08,ZH-Main-Down,Swan Hermit,0,0,0,,什麼東西都不要相信
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.08,0:13:13.80,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,哈
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.80,0:13:16.81,ZH-Main-Down,Swan Hermit,0,0,0,,能夠信任的只有自己
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.81,0:13:18.31,ZH-Main-Down,Swan Hermit,0,0,0,,啊 我說的話例外哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.80,0:13:19.88,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,自己
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.82,0:13:24.65,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,這種事情想逃也逃不掉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.65,0:13:27.18,ZH-Main-Down,Swan Hermit,0,0,0,,好的感謝惠顧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.18,0:13:28.17,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,靜留
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.17,0:13:29.75,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,把這個給他應該沒問題吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.75,0:13:30.69,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,我想這是你父親的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.98,0:13:32.38,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,我們應該用不上這個
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.38,0:13:33.20,ZH-Main-Down,Swan Hermit,0,0,0,,不是不是這
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.20,0:13:37.66,ZH-Main-Down,Swan Hermit,0,0,0,,這難道就是文明的力量 加熱非燃燒煙的煙倉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.66,0:13:39.46,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,嗯 你要的話就給你算了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.46,0:13:42.46,ZH-Main-Down,Swan Hermit,0,0,0,,太感謝啦（多國語言）
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.46,0:13:43.78,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,真的不用客氣
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.78,0:13:45.44,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,照顧好自己 老爺爺
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.44,0:13:46.59,ZH-Main-Down,Swan Hermit,0,0,0,,這裡就交給我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.59,0:13:50.53,ZH-Main-Down,Swan Hermit,0,0,0,,我會沿著高麗川 順著西池袋線而上
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.53,0:13:52.48,ZH-Main-Down,Swan Hermit,0,0,0,,所有的謎題都會一一解明
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.48,0:13:53.59,ZH-Main-Down,Swan Hermit,0,0,0,,欸 等會
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.59,0:13:55.59,ZH-Main-Down,Swan Hermit,0,0,0,,我才不是老爺爺啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.59,0:13:56.99,ZH-Main-Down,Swan Hermit,0,0,0,,我現在還很年輕啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.83,0:13:59.55,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,他是個挺奇怪的人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.55,0:14:02.70,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,但是好久沒有遇見過成年人類了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.70,0:14:04.02,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,除了貓哥他們
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.02,0:14:05.48,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,噢 確實
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.79,0:14:08.95,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,總感覺他像是賣護身符的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.95,0:14:10.10,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,啊 我懂
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.10,0:14:11.71,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,又可疑又虛偽
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.71,0:14:14.95,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,我還是第一次遇到 比善治郎先生還怪的人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.95,0:14:16.31,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,說起來
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.31,0:14:18.44,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,為什麼善治郎先生不和我們一起來呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.44,0:14:20.06,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,欸 不要 和他同行
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.06,0:14:21.06,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,不然睡在哪裡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.06,0:14:23.74,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,你那種鼠目寸光的話就不要說了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.74,0:14:26.60,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,一起來的話 很多事情都能聽他解釋
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.60,0:14:28.94,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,善治郎先生說他不想離吾野
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.94,0:14:29.97,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,他無法離開那裡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.97,0:14:31.20,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.20,0:14:35.77,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,他說他一離吾野 頭痛和頭暈就會加重非常厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.77,0:14:38.36,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,說是因為軟綿綿手術導致的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.36,0:14:39.92,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,也許是暗示也說不定
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.92,0:14:41.02,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,暗示嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.02,0:14:43.02,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,好比是洗腦術或是催眠術
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.02,0:14:43.75,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.75,0:14:47.32,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,軟綿綿的狀態 那麼就很可能是一種暗示
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.32,0:14:49.32,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,但實際上可能並沒有什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.60,0:14:52.58,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,但實際上他頭上確實有個印記啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.58,0:14:54.19,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,嗯 確實
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.19,0:14:57.77,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,嘛總而言之 善治郎不一起來也挺好的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.77,0:14:59.34,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,玲實真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.34,0:15:02.00,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,畢竟增加一個人 儲糧消耗也會增加的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.65,0:15:07.16,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,但反過來說 靜留你為什麼決定要去池袋呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.16,0:15:10.61,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,這種事情 要是書面說明咱應該可以
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.61,0:15:12.29,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,是為了葉香 對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.14,0:15:15.22,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,因為沒有吾野找到她嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.50,0:15:17.82,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,玲實 這種話沒必要說啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.82,0:15:19.28,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,怎麼了 我說錯了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.28,0:15:20.47,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,對嗎 靜留
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.84,0:15:22.76,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,雖然是對的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.76,0:15:24.72,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,是因為在報紙上看到了她的照片嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.72,0:15:26.98,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,嘛 差不多是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.28,0:15:29.26,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,欸 但是你怎麼做
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.26,0:15:30.28,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,不會太勉強嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.28,0:15:31.34,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.34,0:15:33.10,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,去池袋應該會輕輕鬆鬆
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.10,0:15:36.29,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,葉香或許會跑過來說 好久不見 這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.29,0:15:37.32,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.32,0:15:39.05,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,能這樣最好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.94,0:15:41.88,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,聽我說 靜留
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.88,0:15:45.55,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,如果靜留你什麼也不說就離開了吾野
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.55,0:15:51.78,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,就好像靜留失去了葉香一樣 大家也會為你而傷心的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.78,0:15:53.34,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,唔 是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.34,0:15:55.32,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,這點我倒是沒想到
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.32,0:15:55.75,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.02,0:15:59.21,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,那麼 就再道歉一次吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.21,0:15:59.59,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,欸
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.25,0:16:03.69,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,說我們沒必要和你一起來
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.96,0:16:08.06,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.97,0:16:12.82,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,葉香我們也是知道的 她也是我們的朋友呀
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.12,0:16:14.07,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,唔
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.07,0:16:17.10,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,嘛嘛 問題不大
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.10,0:16:18.44,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,不是 咱是真的對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.44,0:16:20.30,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,我沒有考慮到大家
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.63,0:16:22.32,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,你有這份心意就好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.32,0:16:23.09,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,是呀是呀
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.09,0:16:25.00,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,既然事情都解決了 我們現在就回吾野吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.00,0:16:25.64,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,哈
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.12,0:16:27.31,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,你是笨蛋嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.31,0:16:29.13,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,為什麼你會這麼說呢 玲實
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.13,0:16:31.05,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,欸 我們不是要做好準備嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.05,0:16:34.43,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,替換衣物 充足食物 毛毯 還有露營用品
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.43,0:16:37.33,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,啊 要是帶些香薰蠟燭或許會更好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.33,0:16:38.17,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.17,0:16:39.12,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,確實
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.12,0:16:40.88,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,睡眠不足是壓力的來源
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.88,0:16:42.42,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,欸 不是 等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.42,0:16:43.61,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,我們都到這裡了還回去嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.61,0:16:44.49,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,難道不浪費時間嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.49,0:16:48.12,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,但是我們沒有任何裝備 確實是比較擔心的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.12,0:16:52.12,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,再說了 我原本就不贊同這場所謂的旅行
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.12,0:16:55.77,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,那我們回到吾野以後 小晶就留在那看家算啦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.77,0:16:57.62,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,留我一個人絕對不行
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.42,0:17:10.25,ZH-Main-Down,Zenjiro,0,0,0,,小雪姐 抱歉讓您做這些了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.25,0:17:14.15,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,那我要帶上《高丘親王航海記》
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.15,0:17:14.85,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,那是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.85,0:17:16.64,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,玲實不知道的小說
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.64,0:17:17.48,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,啊確實
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.48,0:17:21.39,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,那我就帶小晶你吃不了的墨西哥辣味洋芋片
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.39,0:17:22.76,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,會很好吃的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.76,0:17:25.05,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,學校缺勤也必須要正確匯報
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.05,0:17:28.50,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,實在不行 直接休學或許會更加好一點
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.50,0:17:30.66,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,那麼我們準備出發了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.36,0:17:44.41,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.98,0:17:47.12,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,剛才這裡還不是這樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.38,0:17:49.13,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,水位竟然上升了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.13,0:17:49.98,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.98,0:17:50.72,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,地圖
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.72,0:17:52.60,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,剛剛那個賣護身符給的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.62,0:18:00.59,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,這是什麼聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.40,0:18:05.53,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,啊 摩爾斯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.53,0:18:07.12,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,這個是摩斯電碼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.12,0:18:07.87,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.87,0:18:09.81,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,我忘記讓小雪奶奶幫我傳達了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.81,0:18:10.91,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,摩斯電碼嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.91,0:18:12.07,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,不是不是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.07,0:18:13.23,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,是告訴善治郎先生
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.23,0:18:14.80,ZH-Main-Down,Zenjiro,0,0,0,,沒有回覆
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.80,0:18:17.48,ZH-Main-Down,Zenjiro,0,0,0,,不是說了每天下午五點準時和我聯繫的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.89,0:18:20.35,ZH-Main-Down,Zenjiro,0,0,0,,這裡是吾野 收到請回答
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.82,0:18:24.25,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,欸 什麼意思
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.25,0:18:25.79,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,點 線 線
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.79,0:18:27.07,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,能不能慢點
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.07,0:18:28.70,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,「收到」該怎麼回
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.92,0:18:34.77,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,好快
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.77,0:18:35.64,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,你敲的對嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.64,0:18:36.79,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,不會是在瞎編吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.79,0:18:37.64,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,給我閉嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.30,0:18:41.99,ZH-Main-Down,Zenjiro,0,0,0,,水位上升
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.99,0:18:43.32,ZH-Main-Down,Zenjiro,0,0,0,,也就是說在高麗川嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.90,0:18:47.26,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,電車淹水危險 請開到高出避難
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.26,0:18:47.94,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,他這麼說
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.94,0:18:49.08,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,欸
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.08,0:18:51.25,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,所以我們到底應該走哪裡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.25,0:18:52.21,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,太糟糕了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.21,0:18:53.02,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,等一會
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.02,0:18:54.81,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,光張嘴說話在這不起作用
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.81,0:18:56.81,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,前進或後退 徵求意見
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.66,0:19:03.54,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,吾野和東吾野的海拔高度由國家地理研究院確定 吧吧吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.54,0:19:04.49,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.00,0:19:06.44,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,已經過五分鐘了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.44,0:19:07.69,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,到底要怎麼辦 靜留
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.22,0:19:29.08,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,前進
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.66,0:19:33.53,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,要來了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.53,0:19:34.51,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,就在我們後面
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.51,0:19:36.27,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,冷靜下來 冷靜下來
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.53,0:19:45.29,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,加速
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.29,0:19:46.47,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,快點加速啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.47,0:19:47.79,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,我在努力
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.17,0:19:57.03,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,前進四
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.03,0:19:58.09,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.09,0:20:01.30,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,跑起來
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.52,0:20:22.19,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,我們回不去了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.42,0:20:25.04,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,但這不也挺好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.37,0:20:26.42,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,好什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.42,0:20:27.78,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,我們只能繼續前進
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.55,0:20:29.46,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.92,0:20:32.06,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,香薰蠟燭 該怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.06,0:20:34.19,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,等到了池袋再帶上也不遲
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.19,0:20:35.34,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,明明你只有一千日元
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.34,0:20:36.95,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,借我點錢嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.95,0:20:37.42,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.42,0:20:38.44,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,絕不借貸
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.44,0:20:39.14,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,小氣
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.14,0:20:39.89,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,吶
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.31,0:20:43.64,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,我們真的要去池袋嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.56,0:20:45.56,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,必須得去
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.56,0:20:47.82,ZH-Main-Down,Akira,0,0,0,,我們已經別無選擇
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.82,0:20:48.85,ZH-Main-Down,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,靜留你認為呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.53,0:20:51.57,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,我要去
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.57,0:20:53.41,ZH-Main-Down,Shizuru,0,0,0,,出發 去見葉香吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.43,0:21:47.85,ZH-Main-Down,Reimi,0,0,0,,到東吾野站啦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.21,0:21:55.47,ZH-Main-Down,Resident 1,0,0,0,,呀呀
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.47,0:21:57.05,ZH-Main-Down,Resident 1,0,0,0,,歡迎來到東吾野
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.05,0:21:59.12,ZH-Main-Down,Reisdent 2,0,0,0,,旅行者真的好少見呀
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.12,0:22:00.90,ZH-Main-Down,Resident 3,0,0,0,,真的真的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.14,0:22:05.00,ZH-Main-Down,Keiko,0,0,0,,要不好好來放鬆一下吧
